===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|mt|/ˈʃɛb.baħ/}}
===Verb===
{{mt-verb|jxebbah|pp=mxebbah}}
# to [[liken]], to [[compare]] {{gloss|to declare a [[similarity]] between to things, be it [[actual]] or [[figurative]]}}
#: {{ux|mt|'''Xebbahhom''' mal-ilpup.|'''He likened them''' to wolves.}}
====Conjugation====
* The sound {{IPAchar|/ħ/}} is kept in all conjugated forms. The spelling is {{m|mt|h}} instead of {{m|mt|ħ}} because this fortition has not been generalised throughout the root (compare {{m|mt|xbieha}} {{IPAchar|/ˈʒbɪːja/}}).
